  "title": "Biotechnologist/QA Lab Analyst (1-Year Contract | Leading Pharma MNC) #HTJ",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Tuas</p>\n<p><strong>Company:</strong> Leading Pharmaceutical MNC</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Scope:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform functions associated with cGMP manufacturing operations within the biologics production facility, including working with engineers in set-up and caliberation tasks, as well as performing reword and quality testing related to the production of parts, components and final materials</li>\n  <li>Uses programs like LIMS, SAP, automated control systems to collect and evaluate operating data, which can be used to conduct on-line adjustements to products, insturments or equipment</li>\n  <li>Develop methods and procedures to control or modify the manufacturing process</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma / Degree in related field</li>\n  <li> No experience required, job training will be provided</li>\n  <li> Internship / Exp in pharma industry will be an advantage</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em>Interested candidates, please forward your resume to</em><em><strong> jalenetan@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Jalene Tan</p>\n<p>Outsourced Team</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
